<h3 id="protocol-overview">Protocol overview</h3>
    <p>
  Collection of nine soil surface samples to 3 cm in differing microhabitats, or
  microhabitat of target species, taxa, or groups within the plot for downstream
  metagenomics analysis (generally collected immediately before the soil
  sub-site samples are collected – if undertaking the
  <em><a href="https://linkeddata.tern.org.au/viewers/dawe-vocabs?uri=https://linked.data.gov.au/def/nrm/e3ad3e5b-7c1c-4b59-bdb1-297f707d2ca3">Soil sub-site characterisation</a></em> protocol).
</p>
